&lt;p&gt;The Leibniz Institute of Plant Biochemistry in Halle (Saale), a research institute of the Leibniz Association, welcome applications for PhD candidates who intend to apply for DAAD scholarship for computational scientists (chemists, biologists, physicists, chemo and bioinformaticians).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are offering a three-year position for a&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PhD student (m/f/d) in Computational and Theoretical Chemistry&lt;/strong&gt; for application for DAAD Scholarship&lt;/p&gt;

